Reasoning: The paper discusses the implementation of forwarding strategies for multi-radio wireless mesh networks to improve network performance and avoid interference problems. This topic falls under the category of computer networks and communication (cs.NI). The simulation study conducted to measure network performance also involves analyzing network flows, which falls under the category of social and information networks (cs.SI).
